    • Method Detail

      • getInputSchemas

        Map<String,Schema> getInputSchemas()
        Returns a map of input schemas for joiner. If the input schema for an input is null, the map will have input name with null schema for that input
        Returns:
        a map of input stage name to input schema for all the inputs to joiner

      • getOutputSchema

        @Nullable
Schema getOutputSchema()
        Returns output schema configured in BatchJoiner#configurePipeline(PipelineConfigurer) at configure time. If not configured it will return null
        Returns:
        output schema Schema for joiner
